                          MOVE G-EVRAKNO TO HS-BEVRAKNO(2)
            WHEN 8 ALSO 0 MOVE 9 TO HS-BAGTIPI(1)
                          MOVE G-EVRAKNO TO HS-BEVRAKNO(1)
            WHEN 10 ALSO 12 MOVE 12 TO HS-BAGTIPI(2)
                            MOVE G-EVRAKNO TO HS-BEVRAKNO(2)
            WHEN 11 ALSO 0 MOVE 12 TO HS-BAGTIPI(1)
                           MOVE G-EVRAKNO TO HS-BEVRAKNO(1)
